room_title: Escape room "Mission Aquanaut" by Key and Code Escape Rooms in Reno
room_address: 1180 Scheels Drive Suite B-103 Sparks, NV 89434
room_description: 81 fathoms beneath the Pacific Ocean surface lies Aquarius – one of the world’s only undersea laboratories for the brightest researchers and scientists. They’ve spent countless hours under the surface, researching the ocean’s deepest, darkest secrets and amazing scientific discoveries. But suddenly, the team has gone dark. The control station on land hasn’t heard from them in 24 hours and is starting to become extremely worried about their safety and the volatility of the lab to any water breach, loss of pressure or fire. As the pressure fails and the depths begin to crush in on the team, you must discover the truth, enter the elevator and descend into the deep blue sea in hopes of saving them from a watery grave.
